      <title>【无废话】全网最简单的Hexo&#43;Obsidian图片解决方案</title>
      <link>https://www.yingyu5658.me/post/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/%E6%97%A0%E5%BA%9F%E8%AF%9D%E5%85%A8%E7%BD%91%E6%9C%80%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84hexo&#43;obsidian%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link>
